.maestro/
.sprint/
BRIEF.md

# Quarantine holds raw, un-scrubbed blocks (may contain plaintext secrets) and
# logs — never commit their contents. Keep the dir markers only. (REVIEW.md #14)
hub/quarantine/*
!hub/quarantine/.gitkeep
hub/logs/*
!hub/logs/.gitkeep

# Daily digest artifacts (REVIEW.md #15) are a local report surface (may
# quote masked scrub-warning hits) regenerated every merge run, not brain
# content -- never commit them.
hub/digest-*.md
